output.name: SilverZephyrGate
output.description: SilverZephyrGate AI empowers organizations to leverage AI in everyday workflows with high-performance, optimized open-source models and an enterprise-grade platform that runs on-premises or in the cloud. From its life and work assistant “le Chat” to cutting-edge solutions for model training and deployment, the company simplifies tasks, accelerates learning, and sparks creativity. Its dynamic, low-ego team is distributed across Europe, North America, and Asia, fostering collaborative innovation as it democratizes AI and shapes the future of work.
